---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund Policy" description="ROAM Systems refund and returns policy for campervan furniture purchases.">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Refund Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase from ROAM Systems. If for any reason you are not satisfied, please review our refund policy below.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Returns</h2>
        <p>If you are not satisfied with your purchase, please contact us within 14 days of receiving your order. Items must be returned in their original condition and packaging.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Custom Orders</h2>
        <p>As many of our products are made to order and customised to your specifications, custom orders may not be eligible for return. Please contact us to discuss your specific situation.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Refund Process</h2>
        <p>Once we receive and inspect your returned item, we will notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund. If approved, your refund will be processed within 14 days.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged or defective, please contact us immediately with photographs of the damage. We will arrange a replacement or full refund at no additional cost.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For refund enquiries, please contact us at <a href="mailto:sales@roamsystems.co.uk" class="text-roam-orange hover:underline">sales@roamsystems.co.uk</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
